  <brief_title>Automated Anesthesia During Bronchoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Target-Controlled Infusion of Propofol and Remifentanil During General Anaesthesia Guided by the Index Bispectral: Comparison Between Manual Perfusion and Automated Perfusion During Rigid Bronchoscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
